        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "This **microfinance scheme** aims to empower small entrepreneurs from the **Rabari and Bharwad castes** by offering **affordable loans** with minimal beneficiary contribution. Designed to support income-generating activities, the scheme helps beneficiaries fund small businesses with **95%** of the project cost covered by the corporation, while only **5%** is required as their own contribution.\nThe maximum loan offered under the scheme is **₹1.25 lakh**, with a subsidized interest rate of **5% per annum**. The scheme is intended to improve economic participation and entrepreneurship among socially and educationally backward communities in Gujarat.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- **Loan assistance up to ₹1.25 lakh** for small businesses- **Interest rate fixed at 5% per annum**\n- **95% loan coverage** by the corporation- **Only 5% contribution** needed from the applicant- Promotes economic independence and small-scale entrepreneurship\n\n",
